 implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"AlertComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"alert"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Alert","type":"text"}]},{"text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of borders (","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProviders"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":") and sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemealertcomponenttokensprovider","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeT